Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:39.93,Normal,Ruby,0,0,0,,Lùi lại!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:48.23,Normal,Ruby,0,0,0,,Thời gian còn ít lắm!
